Package: PofOAssignment
Type: Package
Title: Assigns parent of origion to each site in each offspring using family
    Trio or Duo phased genotypes.
Version: 1.0
Date: 2016-05-15
Author: Bharati Jadhav
Maintainer: Bharati Jadhav <bharati.jadhav@mssm.edu>
Description: It has three major steps. 1) zero-out the sites in family with
    Mendelian error 2) use sliding window algorithm to detect and fix phase switch
    error 3) retrieve the genotype at het sites in offspring which were set to
    missing in sliding window and assign PofO using simple Mendelian Inheritance
    Rule
Depends:
    R(>= 3.0)
Imports:
    doParallel
VignetteBuilder: knitr
NeedsCompilation: no
License: Open-source
RoxygenNote: 5.0.1
